Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cosmetics
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:24.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:26.45,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,An irresistible woman~
